      <div type="notes" xml:lang="en">
	<p>This edition is based on <ref target="bibl:K">Senart 1902-1903</ref>. The inscription is closely connected to <ref target="in:K8">K8</ref>.</p>
      </div>
      <div type="edition" xml:lang="mi-Latn">
	<p>
	  <lb n="1"/>
	    <placeName key="pl:Śūrpāraka">sopārakā</placeName>
	    bhayaṃtānaṃ dhamutariyā<app
	      ><lem wit="#K">naṃ</lem>
	       <rdg wit="#AS #CTI">na</rdg>
	    </app> bhāṇa<lb n="2" break="no"/>kasa 
	    <persName key="pers:Svātimitra">sātimitasa</persName>
	  <lb n="3"/>sasariro thabo dānaṃ
	</p>
      </div>
      <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
	<p>
	  (This) pillar containing relics (is) the gift of the
	  preacher
	  <persName key="pers:Svātimitra">Svātimitra</persName>,
	  (of the sect) of the venerable Dhammutariyas, from
	  <placeName key="pl:Śūrpāraka">Śūrpāraka</placeName>.
	</p>
      </div>
